subsection.p:
Add the four sides:
\oint_{\partial R}\omega \amp= (3-b)h+2(a+h)k-(3-b-k)h-2ak \amp= kh+2hk \amp= 3hk.
The area of the rectangle is hk. So \boxed{\oint_{\partial R}\bigl((3-y)\,dx+2x\,dy\bigr)=3\,\operatorname{Area}(R).}

